description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Help the baby mammoth escape the end of the world!  Outrun the avalanche, duck under hungry vultures, and bash through trees in this epic fight against extinction!  Made by SlashStar Games ^^
